          "Code": "player.PlayerTradeComponent.IsReadyToTrade = false\nplayer.PlayerTradeComponent.TraderID = nil\n\t\ntable.clear(player.PlayerTradeComponent.TraderItems)\n\nfor i = 1, 6 do\n\tplayer.PlayerTradeComponent.TraderItems[i] = 0\nend\n\n-- 생성된 Caption Item을 모두 Delete합니다. -----------\nself:DeleteListItems(player.Name)",
